  "title": "Production Operators",
  "description": "<p><strong>Work Life Balance / 5 Days Work Week Options</strong><br /><strong>3 Rotating Shifts / NORTH</strong><br /><strong>Highly accessible / AWS + VB</strong><br /><br /><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><ul><li>Perform & execute day-to-day operation of assigned machine(s): setup, shut down, load & unload, perform simple trouble shooting & minor adjustment onto machine to achieve defined specification (process & product)</li><li>Documents production records: in-process data, end-of-line product data, calibration record, inspection  record, maintenance record, ware house record on hard copy as well as softcopy.</li><li>When required, support sorting activities, sample building activities where some coordination, tracking, running machine & documentation are among the tasks expected.</li><li>Observe & perform good housekeeping rules at related working area (direct or indirect relevant)</li><li>Participate in continuous improvement or cost down projects</li><li>Work in Clean Room environment</li></ul><p>Interested Parties please <strong>WhatsApp us at 8893424 (Jasmine)</strong>, and email your latest resume in WORD format to <strong>jl@businessedge.com.sg</strong>. You may call 65698233 for a private & confidential discussion.</p><p></p><p></p>",
